[music vae](https://magenta.tensorflow.org/music-vae)

Music VAE is an ML model, developed by the Google Magenta team.

Previous projects of this team include [SketchRNN](https://research.googleblog.com/2017/04/teaching-machines-to-draw.html), [NSynth](https://g.co/magenta/nsynth)

Paper is [here](https://arxiv.org/abs/1803.05428)

Implementation are [MelodyMixer](https://g.co/melodymixer), [Beat Blender](https://g.co/melodymixer) [Latent Loops](https://goo.gl/magenta/latent-loops)
